description:
Terrorist Takedown returns for a third outing with Covert Operations, featuring jungle warfare deep in South America.

1) Mount, or burn the ISO.

2) Install the game.

3) Copy the crack from the CRACK folder into the DIR of install.

4) If you want to use Xpadder, copy the folder onto your hard drive and run the xpadder.exe to set it up. 

NOTE: Profiles for Xbox360 and PS3 included; if you're using a different controller, make a new profile from scratch.

